title: Mexican Bean Enchiladas & Sour Cream with Charred Corn Salsa & Guacamole
description: With beans, tortillas, Cheddar cheese and charred yet sweet salsa, this Mexican favourite is colourful, delicious and a heap of fun to make.
Don’t forget to dollop on the avocado to really get the fiesta going!

